name: Sebulba's Podracer
Lore: 'Some hidden modifications mean Sebulba''s Podracer doesn''t conform to race specifications. The duplicitous Dug has equipped it with a flame emitter that can fry other Podracers.',
Text: 'Deploy on Podrace Arena. Adds 3 to each of your race destinies here. If you and your opponent have the same race total, may use 2 Force. Opponent draws no race destiny for remainder of turn (may only be used once for any race total).',
